# PHANTOM AI | The BlackNova Intelligence Core

![PhantomAI Banner](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620712943543-bcc4628c9757?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200)

PhantomAI is a world-class local intelligence core powered by the **BlackNova Engine**. Designed for deep system integration on Windows workstations, it provides a high-performance, zero-latency environment for multi-agent synergy and secure voice automation.

## üöÄ Key Features

- **BlackNova OS Suite**: Localized intelligence that runs entirely on your machine.
- **Voice Link 3.0**: Advanced human-like spoken interaction with sub-millisecond response times.
- **Kernel-Level Automation**: Direct system interaction with ultra-low latency (0.05ms).
- **Zero-Knowledge Vault**: Military-grade AES-256 encryption for all processed data.
- **NPU Acceleration**: Native support for Neural Processing Units for hardware-accelerated inference.

## üíª System Requirements

- **Operating System**: Windows 10 or Windows 11 (64-bit only).
- **Architecture**: x64 or ARM64 (Optimized for NPU-enabled chipsets).
- **RAM**: 8GB Minimum (16GB Recommended for multi-agent workflows).
- **Disk Space**: 500MB for core binary; additional space for local model weights.

## üõ† Deployment

